SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: FRONT PORCH COMMUNITIES OPERATING GROUP REGULARLY AND CONSISTENTLY MONITORS AND ENFORCES COMPLIANCE WITH ITS CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY. EACH YEAR ALL BOARD MEMBERS, OFFICERS AND SENIOR MANAGEMENT MEMBERS ARE REQUIRED TO COMPLETE AND SIGN A CONFLICT OF INTEREST FORM DISCLOSING ANY CONFLICTS OF INTEREST.
